high_descs: Head towards the silver rack to the right of the sink.
Pick up the dirty rag next to the yellow bottle.
Turn left and stand on the left side of the sink, facing the sink.
Put the rag in the sink, rinse it, and pick it up.
Turn right and head towards the silver rack.
Put the rag on the top shelf of the silver rack next to the yellow bottle.
anns.task_desc: Pick up the dirty pink rag, rinse it in the sink, return it.

high_descs: Turn around, head towards the toilet, turn left and head towards the metal rack.
Pick up the dirty towel on the rack.
Turn left and head towards the sink on your right.
Place the towel in the sink, rinse it, and pick it back up.
Turn right and head towards the metal rack on your left.
Place the towel on the second rack right beneath the yellow bottle.
anns.task_desc: Clean the dirty towel on the metal rack.

high_descs: Pick up the dirty rag from the rack.
Bring the rag to the sink.
Wash the rag in the sink.
Bring the rag back to the rack.
Put the cleaned rag on the rack.
anns.task_desc: Put a cleaned rag on the metal rack.
